Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.43,sign_Vertical - R,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有朝一日　一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.43,sign_Vertical - B,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(886.6,541.6)}有朝一日　一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.61,Default,G,0,0,0,,跑这么快　小心摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:43.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:47.12,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:48.28,Default,16,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.01,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:52.47,Default,16,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:54.97,Default,16,0,0,0,,我的名字是...
